Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:16.41,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Only three of you are running\Nunder thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:22.29,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're all \Nable to run a 10K now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.92,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We still have three weeks until the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:30.38,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,20km is the base distance for cross country,\Nbut none of us will drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:36.70,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,On the track, I'm planning to push the build-up\Nruns we'd been holding back on this spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:41.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,so we can finish the last\Nthousand meters in 2:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.17,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:47.92,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You got a bunch of total\Namateurs to the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:52.97,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than good enough\Nto hold your own coaching lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.89,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Making it to the qualifier isn't our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:57.07,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:05.57,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My legs and hips are shot,\Nbut I still have my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:09.04,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.82,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, qualifiers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.38,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your legs and hips still work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:37.95,Series_Title,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Run with the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.94,Kansei_University_02:54(Ep 15),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kansei University
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:00.64,main,CHAIRMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kansei University honors \Nthe spirit of Matsudaira Sadanobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.65,Chairman's_Office_02:56(Ep 15),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.91,main,CHAIRMAN,0000,0000,0000,,who promoted the Kansei Reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:08.07,main,CHAIRMAN,0000,0000,0000,,We value both academics and athletics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:10.29,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.15,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the paper! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.98,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd appear in a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:20.47,Newspaper_03:15(Ep 15),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,“Aiming For the Top”\N10 men take on the Hakone Ekiden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.11,main,REPORTER,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.29,main,REPORTER,0000,0000,0000,,Since you haven't \Nmade it through the qualifier,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.13,main,REPORTER,0000,0000,0000,,getting you into the sports\Nsection might be difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.52,main,REPORTER,0000,0000,0000,,but your attempt itself is captivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.73,main,REPORTER,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have your story run \Nin the local news section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.19,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.61,Yaokatsu_03:38(Ep 15),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Yaokatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.78,Chairman's_Office_02:56(Ep 15),SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.41,main,DIRECTOR,0000,0000,0000,,We're all hoping you'll \Nmake it through the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.32,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could run right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.72,Ep_title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,Place of Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.68,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,My parents called.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.54,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,They saw us in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.89,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,They were so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.56,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,So did ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.60,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,They yelled at us for throwing peace signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:17.06,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,My parents told me to smile more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.14,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,What are your parents like? I can't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.69,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,They're normal. Normal,\Nwith faces that look like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.91,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think my parents are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.97,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so devoted to their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:34.84,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.75,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.69,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we even received \Nan interview request from Nippon TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.38,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:50.23,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know, but the qualifier\Nis televised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:57.92,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,They even broadcast interviews with\Na handful of particularly notable schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.67,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,And we were chosen for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.24,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.10,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't responded yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.36,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.46,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,If the cameras prevented us\Nfrom focusing on the race,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.08,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,we'd be putting the cart before the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.40,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Damn honor student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.00,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,We should accept their offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.04,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be interviewed! \NI want to be on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.48,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll certainly be good\Nfor promoting the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.52,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.76,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.26,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.60,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll send a lady reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.84,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally be popular with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:34.01,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane, Jota.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.71,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.23,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.82,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.16,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:49.16,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Won't appearing on TV cause trouble for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.51,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.35,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,They're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.14,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.00,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.34,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.69,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.42,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, Shindo, Prince, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.87,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:16.88,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,My “maybe” became a “definitely” today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.82,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,The twins and Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:21.56,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:26.78,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you I made a discovery\Nwhen we were in the bath together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.74,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,That attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.95,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,That atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.12,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely those of a woman in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.85,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other reason she'd make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:44.26,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana definitely loves one of the twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.74,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Youth is beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:52.10,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, Musa. Joji, Jota. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.51,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.01,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.44,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,But which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.86,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,They're practically the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:08.19,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so it's one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:22.50,main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.46,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The Hakone qualifier starts\Nat the Self-Defense Force base,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.12,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,adjacent to Showa Memorial Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.61,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start by running two laps\Naround the airstrip and taxiway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.80,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's about five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll head out \Nonto the road, pass the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.26,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and cross under the monorail bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.94,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's about ten kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.40,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The turnaround point is at 11.2 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.40,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,When we return to the park, \Nwe'll have run fifteen kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.24,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run a lap through the hilly park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.53,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The finish line is next to \Nthe Minna-no Harappa Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.29,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,How plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.95,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,I expected the finish line to be flashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.07,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see the day of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.00,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It won't matter if it's plain or flashy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.06,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll announce the results here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:15.43,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is where\Nour destiny will be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.20,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm being soft?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.03,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.50,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have made them run more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.66,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Before I sleep, while I'm eating,\Nwhen I'm in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.76,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,My doubts are constantly following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.25,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have imposed \Nmore rules like a stronger school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.12,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and forced them to run more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.76,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,You can't force a person to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:01.07,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that makes \Na person run is their own will. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.64,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:07.55,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I was constantly suffering\Nwhen I ran during high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.36,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to be\Nrestricted like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.18,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll run of my own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:16.94,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Freely, far away, to the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.27,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.54,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.69,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,People always want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.67,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We have two weeks until the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.52,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle of concentration now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:40.80,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to focus and exercise self-control,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,so we can go into the qualifier\Nin top physical and mental shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.98,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:49.19,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We've trained more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.90,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to turn that pressure into\Na rasp and polish our minds and bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:59.63,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine yourself running as a beautiful\Nblade on the day of the qualifier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:03.41,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,and diligently polish\Nyourselves to a fine point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.04,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,How poetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.43,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.45,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,We should be like tempered katanas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.62,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be screwed if we polish too much\Nand break before the race, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.03,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.59,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your minds and bodies\Nand polish carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:23.56,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Competitions are strange things,\Nand I don't just mean long-distance races.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:32.02,Text_message(10:23(Ep 15),TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call\NMom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:27.26,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You've done the training.\NAll that's left is to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.77,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Or so you'd think, but for some\Nreason, some runners self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:37.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Most things we call mistakes are the result\Nof pressure or weakness of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.13,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.42,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,you can't stop the anxiety\Nfrom rising to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:47.06,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how certain you are,\Nyou still can't erase your fear of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.92,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The more you polish something,\Nthe more fragile it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.30,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,just as a little bit of dust\Ncan ruin a delicate machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:02.66,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,So we must find strength. \NUnwavering strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.88,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,True strength, so we won't\Nbe defeated by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.22,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.07,main,DIRECTOR,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be doing this\Ntwo days before the qualifier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.92,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.25,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.26,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll sit and wait for the next day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.22,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.01,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for a message from our coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.74,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.99,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.68,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll share my secret to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.20,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.06,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,The coach removes the veil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.51,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Alternate using your left and right feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.39,main,TAZAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and you'll eventually\Narrive at the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.11,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.98,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.01,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going\Nto start acting like a coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.47,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.83,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.76,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.75,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.81,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say it didn't feel like\Nit would be no exaggeration
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.30,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,to say he spoke the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.41,main,NICO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.54,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.02,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.89,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Just how carefree are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.81,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, could you bring up\Nsome ice from downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.81,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.86,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.39,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.82,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering me. I want to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.86,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.66,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,My parents saw the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.64,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.16,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen them in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.04,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.52,main,PLASTERER,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have different track suits forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.19,main,JOTA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.24,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,They're a present from everyone\Nat the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.98,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't embarrass us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.13,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,We won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.72,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.68,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're taking our first step\Ntowards winning the Hakone Ekiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.97,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Win? Win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.39,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is he a regular now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.76,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he a first-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.12,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.08,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.11,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but look\Nat the cheerleaders, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.38,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:48.72,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji said they'd make it if their\Ncombined time was less than 10:12:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.37,main,PLASTERER,0000,0000,0000,,That's just over an hour per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.64,main,BUTCHER,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it over 20 km?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.91,main,BUTCHER,0000,0000,0000,,A full marathon takes over two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.91,main,BUTCHER,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have to run like professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.85,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,That's just over three minutes per kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.09,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.28,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, there are no landmarks.\NIt'll be tough to judge your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.44,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's poor, and we\Ndon't know how the race will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.26,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but don't get dragged along by\Nrunners recklessly charging ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.74,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru and I will run in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.61,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Stay together and maintain\Nyour own pace in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.50,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we finish\None lap around the airstrip,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.94,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of guys should start to fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.84,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending signals during the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.87,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose sight of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.73,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.11,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's the ten of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.62,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be here \Nif anyone had been missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.95,main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound like\Nthe final episode of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.86,main,JOJI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.13,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.88,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,There are different numbers\Nof guys wearing uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.41,main,PLASTERER,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.26,main,PLASTERER,0000,0000,0000,,They've got more than ten guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:03.23,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,A team can register up to \Nfourteen runners for the qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:07.71,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Then they'll reduce their numbers\Nto twelve based on their physical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:13.53,main,BUTCHER,0000,0000,0000,,What? So they calculate your total time\Nbased on your ten fastest runners?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:18.14,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Teams with lots of runners\Nhave two runners as insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.93,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what they call a numbers game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.36,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It also means Kansei is finished\Nif a single one of their runners
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.35,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't make it to the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.02,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. They'll all come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:34.58,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.50,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.90,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.93,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.37,main,PRINCE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.44,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.08,italics,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Runners, please gather at the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:08.02,italics,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Runners, please gather \Nat the starting line. Gather round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.88,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:19.14,italics,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Line up by school. By school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:23.19,italics,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Teito Univesity. Saikyo University.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.85,italics,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Sport University.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.92,main,KING,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't our starting position\Nkind of a big handicap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.67,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's based on performance. We can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.28,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,They really are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.73,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they weren't seeded, the people\Nwho ran at Hakone last year feel different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.67,main,MUSA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.62,main,KAKERU,0000,0000,0000,,We're just as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.36,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.43,main,SHINDO,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.90,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains of Hakone are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.14,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,The steepest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.02,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Starting in thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.36,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Starting in ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.32,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.28,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.24,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.20,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,six,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.16,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,five,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.12,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,four,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.08,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,three,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.04,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,two,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.00,main,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.66,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kansei University!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.93,main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.27,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Finish the first five kilometers in 3:10 each.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.14,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,After that, use your own judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.87,main,PLASTERER,0000,0000,0000,,Just two laps of this makes me feel faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.37,main,YAOKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Hanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.79,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,The runners are starting their second lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.33,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.71,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Excuse me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.52,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,The lead pack's pace is 2:49!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.44,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,The lead pack's pace is 2:49!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.34,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them drag you ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.54,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.51,main,HAIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.24,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.71,main,OFFICIAL,0000,0000,0000,,The second lap is ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.59,main,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Haiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:46.04,sign_32625_349_Next_Time__The_O,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dreams and Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.99,main,NARRATION,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Dreams and Reality.”
